INSERT INTO `tvshows` VALUES (1,'Marvel\'s Agent Carter','https://terrigen-cdn-dev.marvel.com/content/prod/1x/agentcarter_lob_crd_02.jpg','data/local/Card Content/tvshow_img/tvshow_0.jpg',2016,'https://photo.cultjer.com/img/cache/width/1000/ug_photo/2016_05/2063720160513125625.jpg','data/local/Wallpaper Content/tvshow_wall/tvshow_0.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/pXMwQQDH8zQ\r\n','https://www.youtube.com/embed//0HGWzkR1jfM',NULL,'The first season takes place in 1946, with Peggy Carter having to balance the routine office work she does for the Strategic Scientific Reserve (SSR) in New York City with secretly assisting Howard Stark, who finds himself framed for supplying deadly weapons to enemies of the United States. Carter is assisted by Stark\'s butler, Edwin Jarvis, to find those responsible and dispose of the weapons.','In the second season, Carter moves from New York City to Los Angeles to deal with the threats of the new Atomic Age by the Secret Empire in the aftermath of World War II, gaining new friends, a new home, and a potential new love interest.','Despite a positive critical response, viewership fell steadily, and on May 12, 2016, ABC canceled Agent Carter.'),(2,'Marvel\'s Cloak and Dagger','https://terrigen-cdn-dev.marvel.com/content/prod/1x/cloakanddagger_lob_crd_02_1.jpg','data/local/Card Content/tvshow_img/tvshow_1.jpg',2019,'https://media.comicbook.com/2018/05/cloak-and-dagger-poster-header-2-1107116-1280x0.jpeg\r\n','data/local/Wallpaper Content/tvshow_wall/tvshow_1.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/zW_4nKoIvbw\r\n','https://www.youtube.com/embed/1_zKJmnVb7g\r\n',NULL,'In New Orleans, Louisiana, teenagers Tandy Bowen and Tyrone Johnson come from different backgrounds and have acquired superpowers after a life-changing event that revolved around the collapse of the Roxxon Gulf Platform. As their friendship unfolds, they soon realize that their powers work better when they are together, they use these powers to try to fix some of the wrong in the world.\r\n','In season two, Tandy and Tyrone work to solve the abductions of women run by Andre Deschaine while dealing with Brigid O\'Reilly\'s vigilante half Mayhem.\r\n','The series was canceled on October 24, 2019.\r\n'),(3,'Marvel\'s Daredevil','https://terrigen-cdn-dev.marvel.com/content/prod/1x/daredevils3_lob_crd_01.jpg','data/local/Card Content/tvshow_img/tvshow_2.jpg',2018,'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/GjMxyP3a-AE/maxresdefault.jpg','data/local/Wallpaper Content/tvshow_wall/tvshow_2.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/jAy6NJ_D5vU','https://www.youtube.com/embed/2Cn3DVV0LHY','https://www.youtube.com/embed/n83s6NO1NE0','The first season sees lawyer-by-day Matt Murdock use his heightened senses from being blinded as a young boy to fight crime at night on the streets of New York City\'s Hell\'s Kitchen neighborhood as Daredevil, while uncovering a conspiracy of the criminal underworld being led by Wilson Fisk.\r\n','In the second season, Murdock continues to balance life as a lawyer and Daredevil, while crossing paths with Frank Castle / Punisher, a vigilante with far deadlier methods, as well as the return of an ex-girlfriend—Elektra Natchios\r\n','In the third season, after Fisk is released from prison, Murdock, who has been missing for months following the events of The Defenders, reemerges as a broken man and must decide between hiding from the world as a criminal lawyer, or embracing his life as a hero vigilante.\r\n'),(4,'Marvel\'s The Punisher','https://terrigen-cdn-dev.marvel.com/content/prod/1x/thepunisher_lob_crd_03.jpg','data/local/Card Content/tvshow_img/tvshow_3.jpg',2019,'https://www.dreadcentral.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/the-punisher-banner-copertina.jpg\r\n','data/local/Wallpaper Content/tvshow_wall/tvshow_3.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/s4QV6OZdmWY\r\n\r\n','https://www.youtube.com/embed/jrLhP5sK2wI\r\n\r\n',NULL,'After exacting revenge on those responsible for the death of his family (see second season of Daredevil), the first season finds former Force Recon Marine Frank Castle, known throughout New York City as \"the Punisher\", uncovering a larger conspiracy beyond what was done to him and his family.\r\n','The second season sees Castle, who has been living a quiet life on the road, drawn into the mystery surrounding the attempted murder of Amy Bendix, forcing him to decide if he should embrace his life as the Punisher.\r\n','On February 18, 2019, Netflix canceled the series after two seasons.\r\n'),(5,'AGENT OF S.H.I.E.L.D\r\n','https://terrigen-cdn-dev.marvel.com/content/prod/1x/agentsofshield_lob_crd_02.jpg\r\n','data/local/Card Content/tvshow_img/tvshow_4.jpg',2019,'http://eclipsemagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Agents-of-SHIELD-s3-promo-5-18-16.jpg\r\n','data/local/Wallpaper Content/tvshow_wall/tvshow_4.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/T3T-evQZiQo\r\n','https://www.youtube.com/embed/PahISq6DKws\r\n','https://www.youtube.com/embed/tx6ws9MAOU8\r\n','The first season follows S.H.I.E.L.D. agent Phil Coulson as he puts together a small team of agents to handle strange new cases.They investigate Project Centipede and its leader, \"The Clairvoyant\", eventually uncovering that the organization is backed by the terrorist group Hydra, which has infiltrated S.H.I.E.L.D.\r\n','In the second season, following the destruction of S.H.I.E.L.D. in Captain America: The Winter Soldier, Coulson becomes director of the organization and is tasked with rebuilding it while dealing with Hydra, a faction of anti-superhuman S.H.I.E.L.D. agents, and a newly revealed superhuman race called the Inhumans.\r\n','During the third season, Coulson begins a secret mission to assemble the Secret Warriors, a team of Inhumans,as Hydra restores its ancient Inhuman leader Hive to power.After the defeat of Hive and Hydra, S.H.I.E.L.D. is made a legitimate organization once again with the signing of the Sokovia Accords.\r\n'),(6,'IRON FIST\r\n','https://terrigen-cdn-dev.marvel.com/content/prod/1x/ironfist_lob_crd_01_6.jpg\r\n','data/local/Card Content/tvshow_img/tvshow_5.jpg',2017,'https://wallpaperplay.com/walls/full/c/8/f/136563.jpg\r\n','data/local/Wallpaper Content/tvshow_wall/tvshow_5.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/f9OKL5no-S0\r\n','https://www.youtube.com/embed/kvvWB0GwCek\r\n',NULL,'After being presumed dead for 15 years, Danny Rand returns to New York City to reclaim his family company from Harold Meachum and his children Ward Meachum and Joy Meachum. When a threat emerges, Rand must choose between his family\'s legacy and his duties as the Iron Fist. After the events of The Defenders, Rand steps up to protect New York in Matt Murdock\'s absence, until a new enemy threatens Rand\'s identity and those he cares about.\r\n','As a gang war brews in New York\'s Chinatown, Danny and Colleen strive to protect the innocent while battling fearsome enemies both old and new.\r\n','Netflix canceled the series on October 12, 2018.\r\n'),(7,'LUKE CAGE\r\n','https://terrigen-cdn-dev.marvel.com/content/prod/1x/lukecage_lob_crd_02.jpg\r\n','data/local/Card Content/tvshow_img/tvshow_6.jpg',2016,'https://www.joblo.com/assets/images/oldsite/newsimages1/luke-cage.jpg\r\n','data/local/Wallpaper Content/tvshow_wall/tvshow_6.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/ORa4hPhGrpo\r\n','https://www.youtube.com/embed/5ogmCV2N9DA\r\n',NULL,'When a sabotaged experiment gives him super strength and unbreakable skin, Luke Cage becomes a fugitive attempting to rebuild his life in Harlem and must soon confront his past and fight a battle for the heart of his city. After clearing his name, Cage becomes a hero and celebrity in Harlem, only to encounter a new threat that makes him confront the line between hero and villain.\r\n','The second season of the American web television series Luke Cage, which is based on the Marvel Comics character of the same name, sees Cage become a hero and celebrity in Harlem after clearing his name, only to face a new threat. \r\n','Following creative differences between Netflix and the series\' writers during the development of a third season, Netflix canceled the series on October 19, 2018.\r\n'),(8,'JESSICA JONES\r\n','https://terrigen-cdn-dev.marvel.com/content/prod/1x/jessicajones_lob_crd_03_4.jpg\r\n','data/local/Card Content/tvshow_img/tvshow_7.jpg',2015,'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jQ7OOzf96gg/maxresdefault.jpg\r\n','data/local/Wallpaper Content/tvshow_wall/tvshow_7.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/nWHUjuJ8zxE\r\n','https://www.youtube.com/embed/rkApe9LqErY\r\n','https://www.youtube.com/embed/7DBKS2qH51I\r\n','Jessica Jones is a super-powered woman who had a brief superhero career until an incident where the villainous Kilgrave caused her to kill someone. After that incident, she became a private investigator. When Kilgrave resurfaces, Jessica must rise up to stop him.\r\n','In the second season, Jessica Jones discovers that her mother is still alive due to the experiments done by Karl Malus\r\n','In the third season, Jessica Jones faces off against an enemy who is determined to prove that she is a fraud.\r\n'),(9,'THE RUNAWAYS\r\n','https://terrigen-cdn-dev.marvel.com/content/prod/1x/runaways_s3_lob_crd_03.jpg\r\n','data/local/Card Content/tvshow_img/tvshow_8.jpg',2017,'https://starloggers.files.wordpress.com/2018/01/runaways-poster.jpg\r\n','data/local/Wallpaper Content/tvshow_wall/tvshow_8.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/embed/y-OJVwUG76k\r\n','https://www.youtube.com/embed/8Y2T3SOlbmg\r\n','https://www.youtube.com/embed/5ReltA7xtbM\r\n','Six teenagers from different backgrounds unite against a common enemy – their criminal parents, collectively known as the Pride\r\n','n the second season, the teenagers are now on the run from their parents, living on their own and figuring out how to stop the Pride\r\n','he third season sees Nico Minoru and the other members of the team face off against Morgan le Fay.\r\n');
